528
00:41:56,390 --> 00:42:02,510
<i>Yeong Eun, I don't want to say goodbye to Ji Min like that.</i>

529
00:42:07,550 --> 00:42:09,560
<i>I'll do it.</i>

530
00:42:11,140 --> 00:42:13,850
<i>I'll braid her hair,</i>

531
00:42:15,110 --> 00:42:18,960
<i>and I'll drop her off at school in the mornings.</i>

532
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:21,060
<i>So let's get chemo.</i>

533
00:42:21,060 --> 00:42:24,020
<i>Even if you'll live for just one extra day.</i>

534
00:42:24,020 --> 00:42:28,780
<i>On that day, unlike now,</i>

535
00:42:28,780 --> 00:42:31,350
<i>do what you want to do</i>

536
00:42:31,350 --> 00:42:35,480
<i>and everything you haven't done.</i>

537
00:42:37,450 --> 00:42:40,770
<i>Let's live one more day, Mi Sook.</i>

538
00:42:41,690 --> 00:42:45,400
<i>Don't give me hope like that.</i>

539
00:42:46,100 --> 00:42:49,200
