731
00:56:03,190 --> 00:56:05,520
I am going to try until I succeed.

732
00:56:05,520 --> 00:56:11,000
You are much more reckless than I thought.

733
00:56:11,000 --> 00:56:12,980
Perhaps.

734
00:56:13,850 --> 00:56:19,970
