737
00:56:30,450 --> 00:56:34,720
But this self,

738
00:56:34,720 --> 00:56:38,390
this foolish and reckless self...

739
00:56:39,120 --> 00:56:41,360
I welcome it.

740
00:56:44,580 --> 00:56:47,300
